lance alignment with human preferences and output diversity. The methodology will include the use of adaptive divergence measures, data augmentation techniques, and new evaluation metrics. Expected outcomes include improved diversity in generated outputs, a simplified RLHF pipeline, and a more effective alignment with human preferences.", role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)'.
